{"tid":1345311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派議員聯署 強烈譴責元朗暴行及警方失職","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T01:50:22.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a6d77d313a753e3ecfc60bd91b0ca9ad619804","tid":1345311,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:48:55.000Z","msg":"元朗晚上發生暴力襲擊市民事件，民主派立法會議員發表聯署聲明，強烈譴責警方失職，令元朗淪為黑社會治港，見暴徒糾眾見人就打的惡行，無法無天。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，暴力襲擊事件令人髮指之餘，更有穿着另類制服的社團人士執行自己一套法律的聯想，情況一如中國大陸的城管欺壓市民。<br />\n<br />\n聲明稱，警黑合作之嫌疑鋪天蓋地。聲明又質疑，如此傷人場面乃是為特首林鄭月娥製造適合條件，為配合政府局部戒嚴的部署。<br />\n<br />\n民主派議員要求立即與林鄭月娥會面，商討解決香港的空前民間災難、以及管治危機。<br />\n<br />\n參與聯署的包括涂謹申、毛孟靜、胡志偉等24名民主派立法會議員。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2196811/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2196811%2F&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=3307c332\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2196811/</a>"},{"pid":"6a6d6e250387af78d7f23ced57529fe11795bcab","tid":1345311,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/22/093123_9f7d9c7c1b682c47a5e249f59bbc821e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F22%2F093123_9f7d9c7c1b682c47a5e249f59bbc821e.png&h=d969c48e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3810525aadffb84b092cdd26b34eb2cbee700f67","tid":1345311,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"呢份聲明係凌晨1點前出嘅<br />\n今次有圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bU3GLx1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbU3GLx1.jpg&h=36f646a6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}